With the Haier HTW62-1187BT Top Loading Washing Machine brings all the exciting features to solve your problems. The semi-automatic washing machine comes with effective usage and adequate tech support which makes it a perfect option for the modern day use and gives a perfect solution for daily use ensuring all your garments are washed according to your needs. Perfectly Equipped for Easy Use With a total capacity of 6.2 kg it washes delicate clothes with care. The Haier HTW62-1187BT Top Loading Washing Machine comes with a rust-free cabinet making sure that the rust of the tumbler doesnâ€™t put stain on your cherished clothes. The castor provide stability and also makes it easy to move around.. The anti-rat mesh makes sure your clothes come out intact and not torn and tattered thanks to rodents. You can also select the level of water to avoid much wastage and depending on the availability because you donâ€™t need a constant source. Spotless Clothes The Haier HTW62-1187BT Top Loading Washing Machine combines utility with convenience efficiently. You get a choice of two washing programs from which you can choose the one that fits you ideally. The machine operates at a high spin speed of 1300 rpm. Having the high spin speed is advantageous because then the clothes take less time for drying and do not require the tumble dryer. Higher spin speeds remove excessive water and helps in quick drying.

product_description: Floral pattern toughened glass soft closing lids: stylish & contemporary washing machine with unique flower pattern. One of the most beautiful clutter breaking washing machine in the industry. Wash & spin lids comes with damper which is super silent, & most convenient and safe to use. F shield strong and durable motor: f-class insulation coating allows temperature to go up to 155 degree centigrade which potentially increasing the life of the motor longer. N9 anti bacteria material: n9 additive is the first of a new generation of sliver-based antimicrobial material keeps the plastic surface safe by neutralizing harmful microbes and resisting algal formation, thereby reducing replacement and maintenance. Memory back up: lloyd washing machines comes with electro-mechanical wash timer enables the machine to start the washing cycle exactly from where it had stopped after a power-cut. 5 wash program: strongest 5th wash program gives extra power to washing, thus resulting best possible wash performance in a semi-automatic washing machine. 2 magic filters: two magic filter ensures better collection of lint compared to conventional washing machines with 1 normal net or magic filter, thus giving more hygiene wash every time.
